Jo Hartley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo_Hartley 0 Joanne Victoria Hartley is an English actress born in Oldham, Lancashire who has appeared on television in This is England and Not Safe For Work, The Young Victoria (2009), Eddie the Eagle in 2016, Slaughterhouse Rulez and "Torvill and Dean" in 2018.
